mods.abstract: Two color window card (red and black on white) announcing Welcome DJ's with George Jones, Jones Boys, Jennifer O'Brien, Whitey Shafer, Brian Shaw, Jimmy Peppers, Gordon Terry, Willis Wade, and Sherry Jerrico. Poster features a metal photoplate of George Jones. For additional information about this poster see https://digi.countrymusichalloffame.org/digital/collection/hatch3/id/25342.
